I'm bored. Avoiding work. And so, here's some One Piece Headers! I just used one wallpaper because I'm selfish and originally just wanted to make myself a header. But I'll share. Enjoy.

<b>~x~ Preview ~x~</b>

<a href="http://pics.livejournal.com/renjiluvah/pic/000525hp/"><img src="http://pics.livejournal.com/renjiluvah/pic/000525hp" width="300" height="196" border="0" /></a>

<lj-cut text="Headers &amp; Code below">

Copy and paste this into your Custom CSS box in your journal style. I'm using a Flexible Square layout. Don't know if that'll make any difference.

<b>Header Code:</b>

<textarea bgcolor="#EAF2EE" cols="50" rows="2">.headerimage {
    position: relative;
    width: 800px;
    height: 200px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    background-image: url('IMAGE URL HERE');
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
}
</textarea>

