As far as credit goes, please give me a shout out in your profile. I'd greatly appreciate it, especially since the images are hosted on my Photobucket page. And if you'd rather use it as a profile banner and have it smaller, here ya go. Paste it in the Bio section of your profile. I haven't tested it, but let me know if it works.

<b>Profile Code:</b>

